description: Take snacks to a whole new level with Heinz Broccoli Fries. These veggie fries make a great alternative to regular french fries and are perfect with your favourite dipping sauce. Heinz Broccoli Fries are a delicious way to enjoy vegetables which is quick and easy to prepare as well. Perfect when you need to whip up a tasty afternoon snack or a side dish for hearty dinners, these veggie bites can be cooked using an oven or air fryer. Best of all, Heinz Broccoli Fries are vegetarian friendly and contain no added flavours or preservatives.Vegetarian friendlyNo added flavours or preservativesQuick and easy to prepareIdeal as a snack or side dishA combination of broccoli and potato in a lightly seasoned batter
